            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>To the underworld spirits of Agathopos, worthy man, farewell. He lived... </p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>As Korhonen notes, the sigma of line 1 could either be treated as part of the abbreviation of Καταχθονίοις, or else as linguistic interference from the Latin formula D(is) M(anibus) S(acrum).</p>
                <p>An online Italian version of this record can be found at <ref target="http://epicum.istc.cnr.it/EPICUM/?page_id=1730">EpiCUM514</ref></p>
            </div>
